Embrace the enchanted Pacific Northwest lifestyle from this .86-acre sanctuary perched above the sparkling Salish Sea. Panoramic vistas sweep from twinkling city lights across Fidalgo Bay to majestic Mt. Baker and the San Juan Islands. Minutes from charming Old Town's galleries and cafs, the ferry terminal, and The Store's fresh-baked delights. Watch orca pods glide past while sailboats dance on sun-dappled waters - all from your elevated vantage in the Olympic rain shadow's perfect microclimate. Year-round outdoor adventures await, from whale watching to island hopping. Visionary developers: transform this prime parcel into 6 residences or 12 cottages (improvements required), or rent while crafting your dream home in this maritime haven.
